                            @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.deposit_Amount, new { placeholder = "Enter Deposit Amount", @class = "form-control", @onkeypress = "javascript:return validFloat(event,this.getAttribute('id'))", Value = (Model.deposit_Amount == 0 ? "" : Model.deposit_Amount.ToString("G29")) })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label required-field">
                                Termination Notice (In Days)
                            </label>
                            @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.termination_days, new { placeholder = "Enter Days", @class = "form-control required", @onkeypress = "javascript:return validDigits(event,this)", Value = (Model.termination_days == 0 ? "" : Model.termination_days.ToString()) })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label required-field">
                                Penalty Clause
                            </label>
                            <div class="gap-3 d-flex">
                                <div class="form-check">
                                    @Html.RadioButtonFor(m => m.panlty_clause_Y_N, "Y", new { @class = "form-check-input" })
                                    <label class="form-check-label">Yes</label>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-check">
                                    @Html.RadioButtonFor(m => m.panlty_clause_Y_N, "N", new { @class = "form-check-input" })
                                    <label class="form-check-label">No</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label required-field">
                                Penalty Details
                            </label>
                            @Html.TextAreaFor(m => m.panlty_details, new { placeholder = "Enter Panalty Details", @class = "form-control required" })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
}
<div class="form-actions d-flex justify-content-center">
    <button type="button" onclick="goToTab(7)" class="@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Previous.CssClass"><i class="@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Previous.Icon"></i>@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Previous.Label</button>&nbsp;
    <button type="button" id="btnBillConfigurationSubmit" class="@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Submit.CssClass"><i class="@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Submit.Icon"></i>Save</button>
    @*<button type="button" id="btnFinalSubmit" style="display:@(Model.isDone ? "block" : "none")" class="@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Submit.CssClass"><i class="@ViewBag.UI.Buttons.Submit.Icon"></i>Final Save</button>*@
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">

    $(document).ready(function () {

        @*var isDone = @(Model.isDone ? "true" : "false");*@
        var savedBillTo = @Html.Raw(Json.Encode(Model.BillTo ?? ""));

        function normalizeStr(str) {
            return (str || '').toString().replace(/\s+/g, '').toLowerCase();
        }
        var normalizedSaved = normalizeStr(savedBillTo);

        $('.chkSelectBillAddress').each(function () {
            //if (isDone && normalizedSaved !== "") {
            if (normalizedSaved !== "") {
                var gstin = $(this).data("gstin");
                var gststate = $(this).data("gststate");
                var buisnessname = $(this).data("buisnessname");
                var address = $(this).data("address");
                var area = $(this).data("area");
                var city = $(this).data("city");
                var state = $(this).data("state");
                var pincode = $(this).data("pincode");
                var country = $(this).data("country");

                var formatted =
                    "Business Name: " + buisnessname +
                    "\nAddress: " + address +
                    "\nGST No: " + gstin +
                    "\nGST State: " + gststate +
                    "\nArea: " + area +
                    "\nCity: " + city +
                    "\nState: " + state +
                    "\nCountry: " + country +
                    "\nPincode: " + pincode;

                if (normalizedSaved.indexOf(normalizeStr(formatted)) !== -1) {
                    $(this).prop("checked", true);
                }
            } else {
                var isDefault = $(this).attr("data-isdefault");
                if (isDefault === "True" || isDefault === "true") {
                    $(this).prop("checked", true);
                }
            }
        });

        // Initial BillTo Fill
        updateBillTo();


        // =========================
        // CHECKBOX CHANGE EVENT
        // =========================

        $(document).off("change", ".chkSelectBillAddress")
            .on("change", ".chkSelectBillAddress", function () {

                updateBillTo();

                if (typeof TosterNotification === "function") {
                    TosterNotification("success", "Billing Address updated!", "Selection Updated");
                }
            });


        // =========================
        // COMMON FUNCTION
        // =========================

        function updateBillTo() {

            var addresses = [];

            $('.chkSelectBillAddress:checked').each(function () {

                var gstin = $(this).data("gstin");
                var gststate = $(this).data("gststate");
                var buisnessname = $(this).data("buisnessname");
                var address = $(this).data("address");
                var area = $(this).data("area");
                var city = $(this).data("city");
                var state = $(this).data("state");
                var pincode = $(this).data("pincode");
                var country = $(this).data("country");

                var formatted =
                    "Business Name: " + buisnessname +
                    "\nAddress: " + address +
                    "\nGST No: " + gstin +
                    "\nGST State: " + gststate +
                    "\nArea: " + area +
                    "\nCity: " + city +
                    "\nState: " + state +
                    "\nCountry: " + country +
                    "\nPincode: " + pincode;

                addresses.push(formatted);
            });

            var finalBillTo = addresses.join("\n--------------\n");

            $("#BillTo").val(finalBillTo);
        }

    });

</script>

